stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created: 创建任务
    Created --> SchemaMigrating: 启动结构迁移
    SchemaMigrating --> SchemaDone: DBCat完成
    SchemaDone --> FullMigrating: 启动全量
    FullMigrating --> FullDone: 全量完成
    FullDone --> IncrStarting: 启动增量
    IncrStarting --> IncrSyncing: Store与IncrSync运行
    IncrSyncing --> Verifying: 触发校验
    Verifying --> VerifyDone: 校验通过
    VerifyDone --> Switching: 业务切换
    Switching --> Completed: 完成
    SchemaMigrating --> Failed: 异常
    FullMigrating --> Failed: 异常
    IncrSyncing --> Failed: 异常
    Verifying --> Repairing: 发现差异
    Repairing --> Verifying: 订正后重验
    Failed --> [*]
    Completed --> [*]
